Ruby SQLite GUI
---------------

Requires:
  - Ruby of course (http://ruby-lang.org)
  - Ruby/Gtk2 (http://ruby-gnome2.sourceforge.jp)
  - Ruby/libglade2 (http://ruby-gnome2.sourceforge.jp)
  - Ruby/SQLite (http://rubyforge.org/projects/sqlite-ruby)
  - ActiveRecord (http://rubyforge.org/projects/activerecord)

Install:
  Linux:
    1. [sudo] ruby install.rb [--prefix=install_dir]
  Windows:
    1. Nothing. Make shortcuts if you wish.

Usage:
  rsqlitegui [options] [database]

For more information, please go to http://rsqlitegui.rubyforge.org
or type 'rsqlitegui --help'
